  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study is assessing the prevalence of aspirin resistance in a cohort of
      diabetic patients. Those found resistant has been undergone pharmacological tests using
      different drug formulations to investigate the reversibility of aspirin resistance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
